question: Within a radius of 190 kilometers, what fast food restaurant is available towards the southeast of Kettlewell & Edwards, Saratoga Springs, NY?
sql:
WITH origin AS  (SELECT ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-73.785108 43.080601)',4326)::geography AS geometry)
SELECT * FROM pois, origin
WHERE ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-73.785108 43.080601)',4326)::geography, 190000)
AND amenity = 'fast_food'
AND degrees(ST_Azimuth(origin.geometry, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN 112.5 AND 157.5;

answers.description: organic ingredients, high end salad and wrap venue.
